        <p class="services-p">The FCA authorisation process involves considerably more than simply completing an online application form.</p>
        <p class="services-p">The regulator may review:</p>
        <ul class="services-bullets ccr009-bullets ccr009-bullets--grid">
          <li>Business plans</li>
          <li>Company structure</li>
          <li>Directors and shareholders</li>
          <li>Controllers</li>
          <li>Customer journeys</li>
          <li>Compliance arrangements</li>
          <li>Complaints procedures</li>
          <li>Vulnerable customer policies</li>
          <li>Financial crime controls</li>
          <li>Financial promotions</li>
          <li>Website content</li>
          <li>Regulatory disclosures</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="services-p">Preparing comprehensive documentation from the outset can help reduce delays and unnecessary follow-up questions.</p>
      </article>

